To install OpenVINO with ESH on Windows, the following packages should be installed before running the ESH installer.
 
Python 3.8.3
https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.8.3/python-3.8.3-amd64.exe
[update PATH system environment variable to refer this version]
 
CMAKE
https://github.com/Kitware/CMake/releases/download/v3.20.2/cmake-3.20.2-windows-x86_64.msi
 
Build tools
[Download and install only C++ related build tools. But try to run samples without this package. If not working then install this]
https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/thank-you-downloading-visual-studio/?sku=BuildTools&rel=16
 

